      "date": "2013-12-20 11:39:50.000000000",
      "message": "Patch Set 1: I would prefer that you didn't submit this\n\nI think a much better idea would be to apply a known bits mask directly in the match/search function. Then it would be future-proof and we won't need to pepper these checks around all callers",
