      "message": "Patch Set 2: I would prefer that you didn't submit this\n\n(7 inline comments)\n\nShadow, thanks for the patch.\n\nUnfortunately, it does not apply to master, since it is based on a parent that is 60 patches and 18 days old.  Can you please rebase it to current master and submit a newer version.\n\nThe changes in statmany.c should be described in the commit comment.",
